It acts as my primary means of communication. It also provides entertainment for me because whenever I feel bored, I often use my phone to watch funny movies. I also can’t live without it because it offers assistance, through it, I can quickly make a call in case of an emergency. Second point: Why shade? I just can’t live without it, it’s like it’s already part of me, like it’s stuck to me or something. If I go out and don’t have it, I feel so uncomfortable.
